â€œDo you know how on movies and TV whenever someone smokes weed they start hallucinating? We all know that's not true, but if you could have a strain that gives you that feeling, it would be this beautiful bud.â€
â€œThis is my favorite strain and I always get it when I find it. The effects are very euphoric, creative and uplifting but it doesn't make me anxious. Plus, it smells like Skittles.â€
â€œOne of my all time favorites, in just a few hits you transcend into cerebral and amazing high. I just picked up some today in fact! If you see it GET IT!â€

â€œI always thought Blue Dream was favorite strain... Not anymore! Super dense buds that will leave your fingers feeling as is they're covered in glue.

â€œmild head high. strong relaxed feeling. mellow euphoric feel. easy on the throat and lungs.â€

â€œAt first glance, I noticed this bud. It was super light green in color with red hair's everywhere absolutely covered in crystals. This strain taste wise reminded me alot of strawberry diesel. This bud looks awesome but it smokes kind of light for my preference. Overall I would give this strain a 7.5 out of 10 rating.â€
â€œThis strain is incredible. Bag appeal was on point. The buds were covered in crystals and very bright like a asteroid. The effects were euphoric and took me to space.â€
â€œThis bud brings two spectacular strains together and defiantly gets the job done when medicating.â€
â€œThis is a fun hybrid that's perfect for live music, the outdoors and road trips!  Delicious and fast acting, it was the perfect hybrid!â€

â€œAroma-  interesting odor, different than LSD, almost chemically sweet, not overpowering.  Works fast, 10 min. in I was felling it. Look - Nice buds, mine were covered in orange hairs.  BuZz - Came on fast, and strong.  I became Richard Dryfus and formed my mash potatoes into a mountain shape.  Tripped to 3rd Kind, awesome movie on this stuff.â€

â€œAt first it was the name that made me interested, me being a syfi nerd it was  going to happen.
